load ../compaction-record-once.maude

--- Coverage: one summarization call records the summary durably.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-COMPACTION-RECORD-ONCE :
  summarize
  =>* recorded .

--- Coverage: after eviction, resume reuses the recorded summary (the record persists).
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-COMPACTION-RECORD-ONCE :
  summarize evicted
  =>* reused recorded .

--- Bite: resume never regenerates the summary. The RESIDUAL soup var means a
--- regenerated in ANY reachable state is a solution, so No solution proves the
--- summarization call is never re-issued on replay.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-COMPACTION-RECORD-ONCE :
  summarize evicted
  =>* regenerated RESIDUAL:Cfg .
